not only for the past but for the perilous present. It is —- as the Times Literary Supplement has declared —- "A remarkable book, a grimly fascinating interpretation of the logic of the Russian Revolution, indeed of all revolutionary dictatorships, and at the same time a tense and subtly intellectualized drama."</span></div></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><div class="ChipList"><ul class="TruncatedItems TruncatedItems--ul"><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/classics" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Classics</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/historical-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Historical Fiction</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--visible"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/politics" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Politics</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/literature" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Literature</span></a></div></li><li class="TruncatedItems__item TruncatedItems__item--hidden"><div class="ChipList__item"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/russia" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--medium"><span class="Button__labelItem">Russia